name: Huseyin Ozkan

description:
Hailing from the "Quiet Corner" of Connecticut, Erik has been at this cartooning thing since the late 90's. While studying Graphic Design, he drew what would become the first Biff the Vampire strip back in April of 2005. A year later, in February of 2006, the Biff site officially went live and he has been working on the strip ever since.

When not working on Biff stories, Erik draws various cartoon characters (many of his own creation) under the screen name 'ProphetEKA' at various online art archives and other such places in-between working on websites and design jobs.
